org.spf4j.base

Interface ExecutionContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, JsonWriteable, Writeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicExecutionContext, ProfiledExecutionContext

    @CleanupObligation
 @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface ExecutionContext
extends AutoCloseable, JsonWriteable
    Execution context information encapsulated a place to store execution related information:
    • deadline/timeout
    • context logs/overrides
    • tagged attachments (profiling info, etc..)
    Author:
    Zoltan Farkas

 @Beta
<T> T get(ExecutionContext.Tag<T,?> key)

 @Beta
<T> ContextValue<T> getContextAndValue(ExecutionContext.Tag<T,?> key)
